{"TopicId":116845,"ForumId":50,"TopicTitle":"KSP Career Mode for Absolute Beginners - Part 3 - The End","CreatedByName":"Phil deCube","CreatedById":120897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-26T01:22:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Phil deCube","CreatedById":120897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-26T01:22:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003EOver the past couple of weeks I posted \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/85cpa\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003EPart 1\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003E and \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/qd84C\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003EPart 2\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003E of this tutorial\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is \u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/LHoNm\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EPart 3\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EPhew! Part 3 was a marathon. It\u0027s LONG, but there is a big science payoff in the end. And it is the end. I think these tutorials should be enough information to get even the rawest recruit to the point of being fairly confident to carry on with the tougher contracts in Career Mode.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#333333;\u0022\u003EAs I said in Part 1:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EOk, so I read many posts from beginners who: \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E1. Have no idea how to start in Career Mode. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E2. Are crawling around the KSC, scrabbling for science points in its different biomes. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E3. Are trying to build aircraft to fly somewhere on Kerbin to do a visual report or something.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EI spent a couple of hours putting together, what I hope is, a useful guide to some of these people on how to go about the early stages of Career Mode.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EIt is not \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003Ethe\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E right\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E way to go about it. There is \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003Eno\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E right way in KSP. That is the beauty of the game. The way is \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003Eyour\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E way. If you want to scrabble around the KSC, good for you. If you like building aeroplanes, fabulous. This is just some suggestions on how you might want to go if those options don\u0027t appeal.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EI hope this is of use to someone. Constructive criticism welcomed.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-07-26T02:31:30Z\u0022 title=\u002207/26/2015 02:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 26, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Phil deCube\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jondugger123","CreatedById":149541,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-14T21:31:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELiterally a second after saying I would like a part 3, i found it. Disregard the last one.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bev7787","CreatedById":136501,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-23T01:09:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s a secret RAAF mission on Duna!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Phil deCube","CreatedById":120897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-23T02:19:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bev7787\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Bev7787\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIt\u0027s a secret RAAF mission on Duna!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWell, it *was* a secret. Thanks mate. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}